message.raw:
SimpleTrackedVehiclePlugin: Flippers ABI compatibility with gazebo9. Do not cherry-pick to newer gazebo versions!

The pull request is specifically made so that if you cherry-pick everything except this commit, you'll get the nicer implementation, which is however ABI-noncompatible with gazebo9.
